Package: purrrays
Type: Package
Title: Functional Arrays, purrr-style
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tomasz", "Kalinowski", email = "kalinowskit@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolbox for working with R arrays in a functional programming style. 
    Contains a family of functions for flexibly splitting, modifying and binding arrays 
    along arbitrary dimensions. Designed to work well with packages purrr, 
    magrittr, and zeallot.
URL: https://github.com/t-kalinowski/purrrays, https://t-kalinowski.github.io/purrrays/
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Suggests: 
    testthat, rlang, zeallot
